%package ps
Summary:	RFC documents - PostScript version
Summary(pl):	Wersja postscriptowa dokumentów RFC
Group:		Documentation
Requires:	rfc-index >= %{version}
# common dirs
Requires:	rfc-ps

%description ps
PostScript version of RFC (Request For Comments) documents.

%description ps -l pl
