%package pdf
Summary:	RFC documents - pdf version
Summary(pl):	Wersja postscriptowa dokumentów RFC
Group:		Documentation
Requires:	rfc-index >= %{version}
# common dirs
Requires:	rfc-pdf

%description pdf
RFC (Request For Comments) documents in Adobe PDF format.

%description pdf -l pl
